name: Eps-nash-algos
body:
A collection of algorithms for approximation of Nash equilibrium. The algorithms
implemented are stated below with their theoretic upper bounds:

- DMP - 0.5-NE
- BBM1 - 0.3819-NE
- BBM2 - 0.3639-NE
- TS - 0.3393-NE
- KS - 0.6667-WSNE
- KS+ - 0.66076-WSNE
